                  <span class="field-content"><a href="/resource/feminist-response-covid-19">FEMINIST RESPONSE TO COVID-19</a></span>

  </div>
      <div class="views-field-teaser">
                  <div class="field-content"><p>As feminists - organizations and activists, working across global movements centered on human rights, sustainable development, and economic and social justice - we have come together in a moment of collective organizing to outline key principles for a just and resilient recovery from the ongoing global pandemic, as well as to track responses and uplift collective action of feminists around the world.</p>
<p>See the full website:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.feministcovidresponse.com/" rel="nofollow">https://www.feministcovidresponse.com/</a></p> 
